      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "DAVENPORT. WASH. Oct. 1.-The\nNTH annual Lincoln County fair open\ned this morning. The vegetable grain\nand fruit exhibits are numerous In\nvariety, and are In splendid condition.\nThe stock barns and poultry coops\nare full of thoroughbred animals and\nfowls. There will be lorse racing\nand amateur contests galore and a\nmidway. The initial days attendance\nIs large."
    }
